{"tid":1470130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爭取遊離派民眾的方法","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:29:33.000Z","uid":177024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95376500024f0d752c2aa84e01dcfbbd2d0febd5","tid":1470130,"uid":177024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"今日we7鋪天蓋地&ldquo;撐HK police&rdquo;<br />\n睇到一頭霧水<br />\n深入敵陣同咗幾個懶係中立ge local/強國人傾計 睇睇距地乜立場：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我唔睇之前發生咩事 我就講尋晚 好過分好暴力&rdquo; - 我地follow曬2個幾月 尋晚發生d事係暴力黎講根本唔算咩level 但距地只會睇單一事件<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;香港警察唔啱 你地就應該學距以暴制暴？&rdquo; - 唔係 警察過分好多 而且警察作為維持社會穩定ge人 標準應該更高 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但原因係距地打從心裡覺得警察有合法性 呢個好難拆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;舉個例 如果警察咁對示威者 我都覺得唔啱要鬧&rdquo; - wtf？你啱啱放出黎？811 d事又唔知 北角個靚仔比福建佬圍毆（同尋晚一樣性質）又唔知"},{"pid":"8735ccab905d0c9dce9d82b00d515f9c1f83673e","tid":1470130,"uid":87541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五點拆局建議（強調係官、警、黨一手造成）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470088</a></span>"},{"pid":"f5d651362f4124cc14f7ca669b763598ffab8628","tid":1470130,"uid":177024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:18:31.000Z","msg":"講中途我有好幾次都好想直接diu9距地走人<br />\n但後尾我就發覺<br />\n原來距地民意唔係咁難爭取 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">距地只係單方面接收信息 加少少理解就以為自己知曬</span></span>"},{"pid":"85042b3206844dc193b5191c82f16220a36f7003","tid":1470130,"uid":177024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"好多巴絲會話&ldquo;都發生咗兩個月 企邊都企曬啦&rdquo;<br />\n其實係 即使發生咗兩個月 坐住食花生ge人遠比你想象多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點樣可以spread到info比呢班人？<br />\n點樣可以平心靜氣d同距地講 你睇得太少啦 更過分ge野(committed by gov and popo)有一大堆？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4261f847ca4b8dd3832f73de9038277b59f0e16","tid":1470130,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"08dfa6aaaadfa51f3940a0b45ef4f77e05c16646","tid":1470130,"uid":177024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"23f9140b7b3aacba42d9529056f676afe89614c6","tid":1470130,"uid":177024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E5%B8%B8%E8%AD%98%E8%88%87%E4%BA%94%E7%A8%AE%E5%9E%8B%E6%85%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E8%25AD%2598%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%259E%258B%25E6%2585%258B%2F&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=492c4fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E8%25AD%2598%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25BA%2594%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E5%259E%258B%25E6%2585%258B%2F&h=52971e9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E5%B8%B8%E8%AD%98%E8%88%87%E4%BA%94%E7%A8%AE%E5%9E%8B%E6%85%8B/</a>"}]}